other.9</p><p>After emigrating to Canada, Musk&nbsp;enrolled in&nbsp;Queen’s University in Kingston, Ontario. It was there that he met Justine Wilson, an aspiring writer. They would marry and have five sons together, twins and triplets, before divorcing in 2008.</p>	Featured	2022-05-25T06:16:51.226Z	2022-05-25T06:16:51.226Z	29	10	85	https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/buddy-boss-article.appspot.com/o/images%2F1653459475562%20-%20how-elon-musk-became-elon-musk_final-43ef802cd2414d14a8bf3967f319ce18.webp?alt=media&token=6260898c-71b9-468d-9c4f-10fc62d908bd	f
